i felt stronger
inside of your  wings
it takes a lot to get home
but its ok
when the light is always on
i just want you to understand
theres no need to keep waiting
another day and another hand
it could be so different
a letter to me your wasting time
you know you could be
yeah you could shine
but tonight youll get it right
you will make a difference
